Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了调查链丹术的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找清国的少女小梅的爱德和阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了她去了北方的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.09,0:01:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲之链金术师金普利追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中央都市向西方前进的斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 斯卡混入夜色中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要从列车上跳车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么弯道较多的这里最理想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为蒸汽机车会减速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是逃向哪边了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡的目击情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里之前一直都很显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南边200米左右的河边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一艘小船被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是斯卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止还没有目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在附近的老人看到奇怪的二人组去了西边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回是西边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上派兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那二个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地图上有一条向北方前进的山道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是去北方地区的林道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为落石不断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在禁止通行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这前面几处和这里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有巨大的落石把道路封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水的流向改变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于善于破坏的链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要破坏这种程度的障碍物非常容易
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的 破坏山体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用落石把路封住也非常容易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链成的痕迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把兵派往北方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}布里克斯的北壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 哥哥居然激动成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过滑了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真是好大的雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在利塞布尔很少能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我们小时候在利塞布林见到的大雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得 记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家打雪仗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也做了雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候完全没有想过自己会到北边来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距开往布里克斯的列车发车 还有一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃点好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然肚子没饿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑步的话又得摔跤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}（各地区…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}（斯卡的手画像呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}（文件号码…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在全力搜查 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目击者称 在前一站的列车调度室中看到像斯卡的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目击情报显示斯卡窜进了去布里克斯的军用列车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同行者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中年男性 头发是黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和报告书一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上让列车停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又让他跳车的话就头痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来就是我的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在北方的寒冷中 想睡也会睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跳过去 请配合好速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了 你已经逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不死心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是传闻中的伊修瓦尔人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能和那些怪物待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跳车的话 就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐鲁夫·J·金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾在伊修瓦尔的干达地区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候在你身边的是家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得有个和你一模一样的戴着眼镜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从左侧腹流出大量的血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚出狱 身体还很僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是因为内乱结束后还一直持续战斗至今
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从体力上说 是我不利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 毕竟只会破坏…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左侧腹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会给你留下向神祈祷的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到两次都杀不死同一个伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让我逃走 这是极大的屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定分出胜负 伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的车厢没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的命令是不准停车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果发生了脱轨事故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 发生了什么事？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说能停下的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向北方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 死就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,构筑死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被死追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远和死相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上灵魂的工作才美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么让人有干劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡先生和尤基先生不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有追兵来追我们 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们吸引了宪兵的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于还没有完全恢复的皮肤来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方的风有点太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能治疗成更好看一点的脸就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 对我来说 这脸才符合我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布里克斯山脉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为和北方的大国德拉古马国之间的边境山脉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该离斯卡指定的地方不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店已经退房了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就在昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道去哪里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得说是要去北方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对兄弟还精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么去了北方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是布里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了 两位小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沿着这条山道走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会到达布里克斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是机械铠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栅栏那边是军队的所有地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没沿着路走会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说山里的天气变得快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到变得有那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全找不到路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兹米师傅在修行时代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被放置在冬天的布里克斯山一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也生还了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里哪活得了一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 据说还打倒了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里克斯的熊如果站起来能超过两米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是国军的军服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子也是机械铠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个平凡的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？倒是你装了个没品位的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道这机械美 真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗用机械铠 M1913-A鳄鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被咬碎的话就乖乖束手就擒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这德拉古马密探
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密探？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不通的大家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个疼痛是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械铠没法正常活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好听人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要反抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下等机械铠我取走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拿走的是你的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等等等 暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么链金术不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是铁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冻死在雪山之前会先被温莉杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用普通的机械铠已经很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里克斯的山岳警备兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 又被枪指着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 帕卡尼亚大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此喧闹 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯壮少将阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯壮是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是阿姆斯壮少佐说要介绍的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥莉薇·米拉·阿姆斯壮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯壮少佐的姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是钢之链金术师 爱德华·爱力克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经中央都市的阿姆斯壮少佐的介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来见少将阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能让警备兵让开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都可以自称是名人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 空的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是亚力士·路易·阿姆斯壮少佐的介绍信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要读了 就知道我们不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是亚力士的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么 你不读吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说介绍信什么的没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要别人给的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用我的眼睛来判断一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 好高 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快走 垃圾们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不走当心我拔掉你头上的天线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说在前头 不会把你当小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是天险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱肉强食的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是斯卡哥哥的研究书
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把清国的链丹术和亚美斯多利斯的链金术融合的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有记载长生不老的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望记载着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会成为希望之书
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说会成为绝望之书
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 让我们开始解读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:23:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里克斯的将军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥莉薇·米拉·阿姆斯壮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激烈 强大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统治北方的亚美斯多利斯的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有被害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.92,0:24:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第34话 冰之女王
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.87,0:24:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识一下布里克斯流
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:12.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因为我犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:16.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}轻微的颤抖着  control过了还在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:20.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}太阳也好  运气（月亮）也罢  完全与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}“只有硬上了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:24.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我这样劝说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:30.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情况很糟糕  临阵逃脱又没毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:34.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}虽然前途未卜  也只能靠胆量获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:37.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}压制着冲动  寻找敌我之间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:40.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是胜利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:43.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}能尝下胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:47.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}或者喝下满腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:51.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二择其一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:55.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操纵命运的轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:00.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}绝好的黄金时间  亲自把握机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:04.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}摆出一副扑克脸  设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:09.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敌人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:16.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}无尽的pressure game  跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}为了跨越荣耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:24.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:29.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底舍不得放弃哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:53.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:22:00.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:03.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}谈话直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:06.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}牵手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:11.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就这样明天后天也一直这样形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:15.98,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看着街上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:21.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个人是无法找到温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:26.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道爱原来可以如此坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:32.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在与你相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:37.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:43.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:48.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为一个人无法入睡  也无法做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:54.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在不安无法到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:59.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是没有星星的夜晚也要继续将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:01.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的话能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:04.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}一个人无法走过的道路  如果是两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼着歌走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:11.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福

